description: Police had been hunting for a man in the Black Forest who seized weapons from officers last Sunday.
title: 'Rambo' suspect Yves Rausch held in Black Forest after five-day hunt
title_page: 'Rambo' suspect Yves Rausch held in Black Forest after five-day hunt - BBC News
maintext: His mother said he was evicted from his rented flat last year. It is unclear if it is the same flat which Bild reported he had rented above a local inn last year, where he had set up a shooting range in his attic.
